description:

www.nuukk.com

name: WE LOVE CUSTOM ORDERS!
description:
We love custom listings!

You don't have square tiles? No problem for us!
Just tell us your size and we'll set up a custom listing for your tile-decals.

These are the prices:

each motive: 5.00€
+
prize per sticker according to size in square centimetres:
1 cm2 = 0,01€

Get 10% off when your order is 60.00€ or more. Don't worry, we will calculate this into the custom listing.

example:

Let's assume your bathroom tiles are 15*20cm and you'd like to have 3 green and 3 pink 'Sixies' decals.

5.00€ x 2 (motives) + 15x20x0.01€ (cm2) x 6 (amount) = 28.00€

Custom-made orders are shipped insured only. 

Please contact us via 
hallo (at) nuukk (dot) com
and let us know what you are looking for.

We are happy to help you embellish your kitchen or bathroom.


www.nuukk.com
